                     <interp inst="t18450203-465-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing 31bs, weight of candles, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18450203-name-363" type="victimName">
